This product is a clean-room-adjacent reimplementation, in Rust, of the
observable behavior of a bounded subset of the Drools rule engine's DRL
forward-chaining semantics. It is developed by differential testing against
Drools 9.44.0.Final as a behavioral oracle; no Drools source code has been
copied or transliterated into this project.

